．．失口先輩は？」"]}, {"box": [455, 1687, 561, 1871], "vertical": true, "font_size": 34, "lines_coords": [[[525.0, 1687.0], [561.0, 1687.0], [561.0, 1836.0], [525.0, 1836.0]], [[492.0, 1689.0], [521.0, 1689.0], [521.0, 1871.0], [492.0, 1871.0]], [[455.0, 1689.0], [484.0, 1689.0], [484.0, 1842.0], [455.0, 1842.0]]], "lines": ["別れたよー", "とっくの昔に", "中学ん時！！"]}, {"box": [118, 1840, 221, 2054], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[186.0, 1840.0], [221.0, 1840.0], [221.0, 2053.0], [186.0, 2053.0]], [[153.0, 1840.0], [182.0, 1840.0], [182.0, 2051.0], [153.0, 2051.0]], [[118.0, 1842.0], [144.0, 1842.0], [144.0, 2022.0], [118.0, 2022.0]]], "lines": ["なつかしー．．．", "プンプンもよく", "憶えてるね？"]}], "img_path": "040.png"}, {"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "img_width": 1445, "img_height": 2120, "blocks": [{"box": [1074, 103, 1113, 260], "vertical": true, "font_size": 35, "lines_coords": [[[1078.0, 103.0], [1113.0, 103.0], [1109.0, 256.0], [1074.0, 256.0]]], "lines": ["「．．．そっか。"]}, {"box": [894, 107, 966, 353], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[933.0, 109.0], [962.0, 109.0], [960.0, 349.0], [931.0, 349.0]], [[894.0, 107.0], [929.0, 107.0], [929.0, 236.0], [894.0, 236.0]]], "lines": ["お似合いだったと", "思うよ。」"]}, {"box": [1250, 536, 1324, 666], "vertical": true, "font_size": 37, "lines_coords": [[[1285.0, 536.0], [1322.0, 536.0], [1324.0, 666.0], [1287.0, 666.0]], [[1250.0, 536.0], [1287.0, 536.0], [1287.0, 660.0], [1250.0, 660.0]]], "lines": ["そんな事", "より．．．"]}, {"box": [739, 579, 879, 795], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[848.0, 583.0], [877.0, 583.0], [877.0, 737.0], [848.0, 737.0]], [[811.0, 579.0], [840.0, 579.0], [838.0, 795.0], [809.0, 795.0]], [[776.0, 581.0], [807.0, 581.0], [803.0, 766.0], [772.0, 766.0]], [[739.0, 583.0], [768.0, 583.0], [768.0, 705.0], [739.0, 705.0]]], "lines": ["さっきから", "言わう言おうと", "思ってたんだ", "けど．．．"]}, {"box": [231, 606, 314, 768], "vertical": true, "font_size": 47, "lines_coords": [[[258.0, 606.0], [314.0, 606.0], [314.0, 693.0], [258.0, 693.0]], [[231.0, 610.0], [269.0, 610.0], [269.0, 766.0], [231.0, 766.0]]], "lines": ["．．．耳、", "貸して．．．"]}, {"box": [312, 1155, 349, 1287], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[312.0, 1155.0], [349.0, 1155.0], [349.0, 1287.0], [312.0, 1287.0]]], "lines": ["．．．あの人、"]}, {"box": [267, 1351, 289, 1498], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[267.0, 1351.0], [289.0, 1351.0], [289.0, 1498.0], [267.0, 1498.0]]], "lines": ["男だよね？"]}, {"box": [1269, 1676, 1306, 1828], "vertical": true, "font_size": 40, "lines_coords": [[[1269.0, 1676.0], [1306.0, 1676.0], [1306.0, 1828.0], [1269.0, 1828.0]]], "lines": ["ぷくく．．．"]}, {"box": [1130, 1809, 1211, 1985], "vertical": true, "font_size": 40, "lines_coords": [[[1161.0, 1811.0], [1206.0, 1809.0], [1211.0, 1946.0], [1165.0, 1948.0]], [[1130.0, 1875.0], [1167.0, 1875.0], [1167.0, 1985.0], [1130.0, 1985.0]]], "lines": ["しーっ", "ーっ．．．"]}, {"box": [192, 1807, 261, 1989], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[227.0, 1807.0], [258.0, 1807.0], [260.0, 1960.0], [229.0, 1960.0]], [[192.0, 1807.0], [221.0, 1807.0], [221.0, 1987.0], [192.0, 1987.0]]], "lines": ["ばれちゃう", "ばれちゃう．．．"]}], "img_path": "041.png"}, {"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "img_width": 1445, "img_height": 2120, "blocks": [{"box": [734, 107, 865, 347], "vertical": true, "font_size": 36, "lines_coords": [[[836.0, 107.0], [865.0, 107.0], [865.0, 347.0], [836.0, 347.0]], [[776.0, 107.0], [811.0, 107.0], [811.0, 283.0], [776.0, 283.0]], [[734.0, 109.0], [770.0, 109.0], [770.0, 287.0], [734.0, 287.0]]], "lines": ["．．．愛子ちゃんは", "くるくると", "表情を変え、"]}, {"box": [596, 105, 681, 383], "vertical": true, "font_size": 36, "lines_coords": [[[645.0, 109.0], [681.0, 109.0], [681.0, 383.0], [645.0, 383.0]], [[596.0, 105.0], [641.0, 105.0], [641.0, 217.0], [596.0, 217.0]]], "lines": ["時に弾けるように", "笑い．．"]}, {"box": [217, 219, 252, 429], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29, "lines_coords": [[[217.0, 221.0], [246.0, 221.0], [246.0, 422.0], [217.0, 422.0]]], "lines": ["そうだな．．．"]}, {"box": [1128, 538, 1266, 778], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[1237.0, 538.0], [1266.0, 538.0], [1266.0, 720.0], [1237.0, 720.0]], [[1202.0, 540.0], [1231.0, 540.0], [1231.0, 720.0], [1202.0, 720.0]], [[1163.0, 538.0], [1192.0, 538.0], [1192.0, 778.0], [1163.0, 778.0]], [[1128.0, 538.0], [1157.0, 538.0], [1157.0, 648.0], [1128.0, 648.0]]], "lines": ["：今の彼氏は", "矢口先輩とは", "全然違うタイプの", "人かなー"]}, {"box": [1035, 658, 1213, 1111], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[1132.0, 658.0], [1153.0, 658.0], [1153.0, 718.0], [1132.0, 718.0]], [[1184.0, 890.0], [1213.0, 890.0], [1213.0, 1070.0], [1184.0, 1070.0]], [[1146.0, 890.0], [1175.0, 890.0], [1175.0, 1070.0], [1146.0, 1070.0]], [[1109.0, 888.0], [1138.0, 888.0], [1138.0, 1111.0], [1109.0, 1111.0]], [[1072.0, 888.0], [1101.0, 888.0], [1101.0, 1101.0], [1072.0, 1101.0]], [[1035.0, 890.0], [1064.0, 890.0], [1064.0, 1072.0], [1035.0, 1072.0]]], "lines": ["．．．", "そもそも年が", "結構上だから", "当然なんだけど、", "常識も理解力も", "あってさ．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [628, 605, 770, 878], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[739.0, 606.0], [768.0, 606.0], [768.0, 834.0], [739.0, 834.0]], [[701.0, 606.0], [730.0, 606.0], [730.0, 877.0], [701.0, 877.0]], [[664.0, 606.0], [693.0, 606.0], [693.0, 846.0], [664.0, 846.0]], [[629.0, 606.0], [656.0, 606.0], [656.0, 799.0], [629.0, 799.0]]], "lines": ["．．．あ、でもそんな", "お金は持ってないよ", "普通の中小企業の", "会社員だから。"]}, {"box": [173, 921, 314, 1227], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31, "lines_coords": [[[285.0, 925.0], [314.0, 925.0], [314.0, 1198.0], [285.0, 1198.0]], [[244.0, 921.0], [279.0, 921.0], [279.0, 1211.0], [244.0, 1211.0]], [[211.0, 923.0], [240.0, 923.0], [240.0, 1227.0], [211.0, 1227.0]], [[173.0, 923.0], [202.0, 923.0], [202.0, 1209.0], [173.0, 1209.0]]], "lines": ["けど私がこんな風で", "基本甘ったれだから、", "ちゃんと叱ってくれる", "人で助かってるんだ。"]}, {"box": [138, 1304, 320, 1577], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31, "lines_coords": [[[285.0, 1304.0], [320.0, 1304.0], [320.0, 1459.0], 